A vast medieval stone cathedral looms dominant over a futuristic abandoned cityscape, its gothic spires piercing through smog-filled skies. Crumbling skyscrapers with shattered glass windows are being slowly consumed by creeping ivy and moss. In the foreground, a massive hourglass lies on its side, sand spilling out onto cracked concrete where small green shoots emerge. The lighting is dramatic and ominous, with rays of dusty sunlight breaking through storm clouds, casting long shadows. Scattered throughout the scene are rusted remnants of modern technology—satellites, solar panels, wind turbines—half-buried and forgotten. The color palette blends cold steel grays and deep shadows with warm amber torch light emanating from the cathedral windows. Cyberpunk style with high contrast, gritty textures, and a sense of civilizational reversal and entropy.
